==Design==
(not all the way implemented)

bin/wikiki command line script to modify the wiki. 
bin/wikiki-dump tool to dump the wiki to html for easy publishing (to dropbox or something)
src/app.py server to host the server
store.sqlite3 - database for pages

src/templates/entry.html - Theme individual pages
src/templates/index.html - Theme the main page.
static/* whatever CSS files you want

Main ideas:
1. keep store.sqlite3 under version control.
2. command line access

Goals:
1. Minimize dependencies
2. Intuitive command line options.
3. The unix way.

